504
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:48,920
If you encounter this kind of thing next time,

505
00:31:49,199 --> 00:31:50,079
tell me as soon as possible

506
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,160
and hide.

507
00:31:51,520 --> 00:31:52,280
I'll help you fight.

508
00:31:56,760 --> 00:31:58,439
OK.

509
00:31:59,959 --> 00:32:00,680
So good-looking.

510
00:32:05,040 --> 00:32:08,040
Do you have anything you really want to do?

511
00:32:10,119 --> 00:32:12,680
Nothing specifically.

512
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,520
Then

513
00:32:16,199 --> 00:32:18,119
let's do what I especially want to do.

514
00:32:19,800 --> 00:32:21,640
What do you want to do?

515
00:32:23,119 --> 00:32:26,119
Watch a movie

516
00:32:32,239 --> 00:32:32,800
with you.

517
00:32:35,599 --> 00:32:36,280
That's it?

518
00:32:37,400 --> 00:32:38,119
No problem.

519
00:32:38,239 --> 00:32:39,160
Let's go back early today

520
00:32:39,280 --> 00:32:40,239
and watch the movie together tomorrow.

521
00:32:40,599 --> 00:32:41,400
It's on me.

522
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:44,599
I'm used to it.

523
00:32:44,599 --> 00:32:45,520
I mean

524
00:32:45,520 --> 00:32:46,359
I'll buy you ticket

525
00:32:46,560 --> 00:32:48,160
and you buy me popcorn, okay?

526
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:49,520
OK.

527
00:32:57,479 --> 00:32:59,199
What are you doing? Arresting the prisoner?

528
00:32:59,199 --> 00:33:00,239
Easy.

529
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:04,239
Let's go.

530
00:33:11,760 --> 00:33:13,479
Come on, cheers.

531
00:33:20,239 --> 00:33:21,319
Today is really a good day.

532
00:33:22,520 --> 00:33:24,839
We finally have the opportunity to be with white...

533
00:33:25,079 --> 00:33:26,520
No, we can't call you white-collar.

534
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:28,239
We have dinner with our sister-in-law.

535
00:33:29,280 --> 00:33:30,800
To be honest,

536
00:33:31,199 --> 00:33:33,000
since the last time you came to our bar

537
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:34,880
and broke Momo's game record,

538
00:33:35,160 --> 00:33:37,280
I said this girl is unusual.

539
00:33:37,599 --> 00:33:38,199
Right?

540
00:33:38,599 --> 00:33:40,359
Only this kind of unusual girl

541
00:33:40,439 --> 00:33:41,680
