543
00:33:43,719 --> 00:33:44,439
So right.

544
00:33:44,439 --> 00:33:45,839
Since you know she's your sister-in-law,

545
00:33:45,839 --> 00:33:48,599
be careful not to talk too much in the future.

546
00:33:49,599 --> 00:33:51,119
Come on, let's eat.

547
00:33:51,319 --> 00:33:52,000
Come on.

548
00:33:54,959 --> 00:33:55,760
Come on.

549
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:57,280
Thank you.

550
00:33:59,119 --> 00:34:00,239
Such a nice dinner.

551
00:34:00,319 --> 00:34:01,079
Boss...

552
00:34:01,359 --> 00:34:03,040
Same sauces?

553
00:34:05,199 --> 00:34:05,719
OK.

554
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:08,319
How mincing you are!

555
00:34:09,599 --> 00:34:10,560
Mincing.

556
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:12,319
Although Lao Luo looks like this now,

557
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:14,920
he is the one who has done
the greatest business among us.

558
00:34:14,920 --> 00:34:15,959
What do I look like?

559
00:34:15,959 --> 00:34:17,079
Look in the mirror.

560
00:34:17,560 --> 00:34:18,280
It's him.

561
00:34:18,719 --> 00:34:20,359
When he started this hot pot restaurant,

562
00:34:20,520 --> 00:34:22,160
he just wanted to open a canteen for the band

563
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:23,920
but he didn't expect that it's getting bigger and bigger.

564
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:26,199
You see, I opened a canteen

